    "Especially ML and DLbased models are discussed in detail.",
    "These models are designed to detect vegetable diseases in various plant species.",
    "• We discussed the AI based plant disease classification, where, the automated approaches to classify disease in each respective vegetable are provided.",
    "• Finally, the challenges associated with applying AI models in disease detection are described in-depth and underlined in this study.",
    "Our thorough study focused mainly on the use of automated strategies to diagnose plant diseases."
